From Wikipedia, the free encyclopedia

(Redirected from [List of countries by population (United Nations)](/w/index.php?title=List_of_countries_by_population_(United_Nations)&redirect=no "List of countries by population (United Nations)"))

UNSD list of countries and territories ries by population

[![](//upload.wikimedia.org/wikipedia/commons/thumb/0/08/United_Nations_geographical_subregions.png/500px-United_Nations_geographical_subregions.png)](/wiki/File:United_Nations_geographical_subregions.png)

*Statistical subregions as [defined by](/wiki/United_Nations_geoscheme "United Nations geoscheme") the [United Nations Statistics Division](/wiki/United_Nations_Statistics_Division "United Nations Statistics Division")[[1]](#cite_note-UNregions-1)*

This is the list of [countries](/wiki/List_of_sovereign_states "List of sovereign states") and other [inhabited territories](/wiki/Dependent_territory "Dependent territory") of the world by estimated total population. It is based on estimates published
 by the [United Nations](/wiki/United_Nations "United Nations") in the
 2024 revision of *[World Population Prospects](/wiki/World_Population_Prospects "World Population Prospects")*. It presents population estimates from 1950 to the present.[[2]](#cite_note-UN-2)

## List ##

[[edit](/w/index.php?title=List_of_countries_and_dependencies_by_population_(United_Nations)&action=edit&section=1 "Edit section: List")]

Data are mid-year estimates from the United Nations and are for 2022 and
 2023.[[2]](#cite_note-UN-2)

