2. **[↑](#cite_ref-4)** Including *![](//upload.wikimedia.org/wikipedia/commons/thumb/d/d4/Flag_of_Zanzibar.svg/40px-Flag_of_Zanzibar.svg.png) [Zanzibar](/wiki/Zanzibar "Zanzibar")*.
